"macroclasses. Check :guilabel:`Use` |checkbox| :guilabel:`C ID` and in "
":ref:`classification_alg` select the :guilabel:`Spectral Angle Mapping`. "
"The :guilabel:`input band set` is 1 because it is the number of the band "
"set containing the image (bands) that we want to classify."
